se.softhouse.jargo

Class ParsedArguments

  • java.lang.Object
    • se.softhouse.jargo.ParsedArguments

  • @Immutable
public final class ParsedArguments
extends Object
    Holds parsed arguments for a CommandLineParser.parse(String...) invocation. Use get(Argument) to fetch a parsed command line value.
